title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show MAY-29-2014 THURS
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show MAY-29-2014 THURS...PODCAST



Dennis Prager Radio Show
Prager 20140529  3 Camille

Prager H3: Dennis talks to Camille Pagilia, 
             renowned social critic and Professor of Humanities
              & Media Studies at the University of the Arts in Philadelphia.

       A Best of Prager Hour. Originally broadcast on January 9, 2014


Prager 20140529  2 Decade

Prager H2: Dennis poses an intriguing question. 
            Is there a decade of your life you remember best?
        
         Another question emerges from this discussion: 
           can you identify a transformational year? 

         Callers weigh in. 


         A Best of Prager Hour. Originally broadcast on November 12, 2009.


Prager 20140529  1 Kitty

Prager H1: Dennis talks to investigative journalist, Kevin Cook.

        His new book is Kitty Genovese: 
              The Murder, the Bystanders, the Crime that Changed America.
